Q_{\alpha\alpha} & Q_{\alpha z}\\
Q_{z\alpha} & Q_{zz}
\end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{cc}
V_{\alpha} & 0\\
0 & V_{z}
\end{array}\right)\\
